d%9c%e6%b5%81%e4%ba%a7%e5%93%81','','','2013-07-17 14:40:47','2013-07-17 06:40:47','',80,'http://localhost/wedosite/?page_id=84',0,'page','',0),(85,1,'2013-03-21 13:33:51','2013-03-21 05:33:51','<!--:zh--><h3>维度云存储服务</h3>\r\n<a href=\"http://localhost/wedosite/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/disk1.png\"><img src=\"http://localhost/wedosite/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/disk1.png\" alt=\"disk1\" width=\"650\"   class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-232\" /></a>\r\n<h3>基本功能</h3>\r\n<p class=\"indent\">\r\n    <h5>个人数据存取</h5>\r\n   <p>OwnDisk 在服务器上保存个人的文件、文件夹、联系 人信息、图片库、日历等;可以在个人的移动设备、桌 面计算机、浏览器中随时随地的按需存取个人文档。</p>\r\n <h5>个人数据同步</h5>\r\n<p>OwnDisk 随时将个人文件、联系人信息、图片库、日 历等同步到个人的设备上,你可以在计算机桌面、web 客户端、移动应用上随时获得最新版本的文档</p>\r\n <h5>个人数据共享</h5>\r\n<p>OwnDisk 可以将个人文档、图片、日历、音乐等任何 数据共享给他人,有两种共享方式可供选择:公共和私 人。我的数据我做主。</p>\r\n\r\n <h5>版本控制</h5>\r\n<p>OwnDisk 的版本控制功能可以自动保存以前的文档并 添加版本号,你可以很方便的查找以前的旧版本文档</p>\r\n <h5>数据加密</h5>\r\n<p>OwnDisk 可以使用加密口令加密个人保存在服务器上 的所有文档;使用 SSL 链接,可以同时保证数据传输 过程的安全</p>\r\n <h5>文档拖拉上载</h5>\r\n<p>OwnDisk 允许个人从桌面拖拉文件到浏览器中的 OwnDisk 文件夹,文件会被自动上载到服务器</p>\r\n <h5>界面样式自定义</h5>\r\n<p>OwnDisk 允许个人定制自己的界面样式,包括背景图 片、字体、颜色、按钮等</p>\r\n <h5>ODF 文件查看器</h5>\r\n<p>OwnDisk 可以浏览器中在线打开 ODF 格式的文档,如:. odt,.odp,.ods,不需要下载到本地打开</p>\r\n\r\n <h5>应用程序 API </h5>\r\n<p>OwnDisk API 允许第三方开发 OwnDisk 的扩展应用, 增加其功能。<p>\r\n<h5>文档的迁移和备份</h5>\r\n<p>OwnDisk 可以很方便的将个人数据备份和迁移,满足 用户对重要文档多份拷贝的需求<p>\r\n<h5>待办任务</h5>\r\n<p>OwnDisk 可以将个人待办任务同步到 OwnDisk 上, 保证个人的待办任务在所有设备上信息一致<p>\r\n<h5>应用程序商店</h5>\r\n<p>OwnDisk 可以十分方便的从应用程序商店下载你所需 的应用并安装到你的 OwnDisk 上。<p>\r\n<h5> 个人日历</h5>\r\n<p>OwnDisk 可以将个人日历共享给他人,这样你的同事 或者朋友就知晓你重要的日历和事件,方便和你约定会 议和工作沟通<p>\r\n<h5>文件共享通知</h5>\r\n<p>OwnDisk 在文件共享时会通知共享者,个人可以快捷 地共享自己的文档、电影、音乐等任何需要共享的信息<p>\r\n<h5>个人相册</h5>\r\n<p>OwnDisk 可以指定个人相册目录并可对相册照片排序, 您可以通过他人的邮件地址共享个人相册,同时控制相 册的共享权限<p>\r\n<h5>同步外部网盘</h5>\r\n<p>OwnDisk 可 以 将 公 网 上 的 个 人 网 盘(如 Gdrive, DropBox)作为一个文件夹存放在 OwnDisk 中,这样 可以通过 OwnDisk 访问所有的个人文档内容。<p>\r\n<h5> 网盘日志</h5>\r\nOwnDisk 可以方便的设置是否记录网盘日志,方便 OwnDisk 进行操作跟踪<p>\r\n<h5> LDAP / Active Directory</h5>\r\nOwnDisk 允许管理员管理 LDAP 或者 AD 中的用户和 用户组在 OwnDisk 中的权限,同时支持 OAuth 的认 证和授权方式。<p>\r\n\r\n</p>\r\n<!--:-->','<!--:en-->OwnDisk<!--:--><!--:zh-->维度云存储服务<!--:-->','','publish','open','open','','%e6%8a%a5%e9%94%80%e6%b5%81%e7%a8%8b','','','2013-07-17 11:28:43','2013-07-17 03:28:43','',80,'http://localhost/wedosite/?page_id=85',0,'page','',0),(86,1,'2013-03-21 13:34:35','2013-03-21 05:34:35','','<!--:en-->Solutions<!--:--><!--:zh-->解决方案<!--:-->','','trash','open','open','','%e8%a7%a3%e5%86%b3%e6%96%b9%e6%a1%88','','','2013-07-17 10:13:51','2013-07-17 02:13:51','',80,'http://localhost/wedosite/?page_id=86',0,'page','',0),(87,1,'2013-03-21 13:35:48','2013-03-21 05:35:48','','<!--:en-->Solutions<!--:--><!--:zh-->解决方案<!--:-->','','inherit','open','open','','86-autosave','','','2013-03-21 13:35:48','2013-03-21 05:35:48','',86,'http://localhost/wedosite/?p=87',0,'revision','',0),(100,1,'2013-03-20 17:39:31','2013-03-20 09:39:31','<h3>The Security Solutions</h3>\r\n<p style=\"font-size:14px; font-weight:bold;\">\r\nPhysical. Virtual. Cloud. Your IT infrastructure is changing to support the needs of the business – and you’ve got to squeeze every drop of value from your investments. When it comes to delivering efficiency and optimizing computing capacity, no IT management software company does that better than Quest. Our integrated portfolio of solutions simplifies the management of your physical, virtual and cloud infrastructures to reduce costs and improve efficiency.\r\n</p>\r\n<div class=\"frame_left img-border zoom\">\r\n<a class=\"\" href=\"/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/quest.png\" rel=\"prettyPhoto\" title=\"This is the description\">\r\n<img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/quest.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"visibility: visible; opacity: 1;\">\r\n</a>\r\n<span class=\"image-desc\">Quest</span>\r\n</div>\r\n<h5>Quest</h5>\r\n<p>\r\nQuest is the market leader in virtualization and cloud management, with solutions spanning server virtualization, desktop virtualization, and cloud automation that support multiple hypervisor platforms.\r\n</p>','<!--:en-->itmanagerment<!--:--><!--:zh-->IT 管理<!--:-->','','inherit','open','open','','58-revision-4','','','2013-03-20 17:39:31','2013-03-20 09:39:31','',58,'http://localhost/wedosite/?p=100',0,'revision','',0),(101,1,'2013-03-20 17:39:42','2013-03-20 09:39:42','<h3>Cloud Networking Platform</h3>\r\n<p>Servers, storage and networks form the anchors of today\'s IT infrastructure. Companies around the world are constantly seeking to enhance this infrastructure. With 10GbE connectivity the new infrastructure requirements are distinctive and differ in many ways from the needs of traditional enterprise IT needs. The new environments often require unique compute density, power density and ultra low latency. Such hyper-scale computing environments – where deployments are measured by up to millions of servers, storage and networking equipment – are changing the way they approach IT to drive growth and decrease operational expenses.</p>\r\n<h5>Overview</h5>\r\n<ul class=\"normal\"><li>Scalable: Cloud Networks scale to thousands of nodes and provide a non-blocking fabric across the entire cloud.</li> <li>Low Latency: Latency is key to improving application performance. The network needs to provide ultra-low latency in a large-scale environment.</li> <li>Guaranteed Delivery: The cloud must provide predictable and reliable performance to a large number services, including HPC applications, web, video and data.</li> <li>Extensible Management: Cloud Networks cross all traditional boundaries between servers, enterprise networks, and service provider networks. They need to be managed in a hybrid environment, often with customizations that are unique to that individual deployment. The management of the network needs to be extensible and customizeable to allow such applications.</li> <li>Self-Healing Resiliency: With larger scale, networks become much more critical and faults need to be contained and healed automatically.</li> </ul>\r\n<hr class=\"hr-sidebar\">\r\n<div class=\"frame_left img-border zoom\">\r\n<a class=\"\" href=\"/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/arista.png\" rel=\"prettyPhoto\" title=\"\">\r\n<img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/arista.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"visibility: visible; opacity: 1;\">\r\n</a>\r\n<span class=\"image-desc\">Arista Networks</span>\r\n</div>\r\n<h5>Cloud Solution With Arista Networks</h5>\r\n<p>\r\nArista Networks is the leader in building scalable high-performance and ultra-low-latency networks for today\'s data center and cloud computing environments.\r\nPurpose-built hardware, and Arista EOS,\r\nthe world\'s most advanced network operating system,\r\nprovide single-binary system images across all platforms,\r\nmaximum system uptime, stateful fault repair,\r\nZero Touch Provisioning, Latency Analysis and a fully accessible Linux Shell.\r\nArista Ethernet switches are the perfect network solution for your most demanding workloads\r\n.With native support for VMware Virtualization and hundreds of Linux applications integrated into hardware platforms designed to meet the stringent power and cooling requirements of today’s most demanding data centers, Arista delivers the most efficient and best performing 10Gb Ethernet platforms.</p>\r\n<p></p>\r\n<div style=\"clear:both\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"frame_left img-border zoom\">\r\n<a class=\"\" href=\"/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/cisco.png\" rel=\"prettyPhoto\" title=\"This is the description\">\r\n<img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/cisco.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"visibility: visible; opacity: 1;\">\r\n</a>\r\n<span class=\"image-desc\">Cisco</span>\r\n</div>\r\n<h5>Cisco</h5>\r\n<p>\r\nCisco Virtualization Experience Infrastructure (VXI) is an end-to-end systems approach that delivers the next generation virtual workspace by unifying virtual desktops, voice, and video. It helps IT provide an exceptionally flexible and secure converged infrastructure for an uncompromised user experience.\r\