icient IT infrastructure that will grow with your business.\r\n</p>\r\n<div style=\"clear:both\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"frame_left img-border zoom\">\r\n<a class=\"\" href=\"/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/fusionio.png\" rel=\"prettyPhoto\" title=\"This is the description\">\r\n<img src=\"/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/fusionio.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"visibility: visible; opacity: 1;\">\r\n</a>\r\n<span class=\"image-desc\">Fusion-IO</span>\r\n</div>\r\n<h5>Fusion-IO</h5>\r\n<p>\r\nFusion’s ioMemory tier moves terabytes of process-critical data into servers, close to application processors. This minimizes latency and maximizes performance to increase the value you provide your end-users, while lowering your infrastructure capital and operating costs.\r\n</p>','<!--:en-->storage<!--:--><!--:zh-->存储设备<!--:-->','','inherit','open','open','','44-revision-6','','','2013-03-20 17:40:17','2013-03-20 09:40:17','',44,'http://localhost/wedosite/?p=103',0,'revision','',0),(115,1,'2013-03-21 14:21:18','2013-03-21 06:21:18','','<!--:en-->Home<!--:--><!--:zh-->首页<!--:-->','','publish','open','open','','%e9%a6%96%e9%a1%b5','','','2013-07-17 14:39:17','2013-07-17 06:39:17','',0,'http://localhost/wedosite/?p=115',1,'nav_menu_item','',0),(116,1,'2013-03-21 14:21:18','2013-03-21 06:21:18',' ','','','publish','open','open','','116','','','2013-07-17 14:39:17','2013-07-17 06:39:17','',0,'http://localhost/wedosite/?p=116',10,'nav_menu_item','',0),(117,1,'2013-03-21 14:21:18','2013-03-21 06:21:18',' ','','','publish','open','open','','117','','','2013-07-17 14:39:17','2013-07-17 06:39:17','',0,'http://localhost/wedosite/?p=117',7,'nav_menu_item','',0),(121,1,'2013-03-21 14:21:18','2013-03-21 06:21:18',' ','','','publish','open','open','','121','','','2013-07-17 14:39:17','2013-07-17 06:39:17','',0,'http://localhost/wedosite/?p=121',12,'nav_menu_item','',0),(122,1,'2013-03-21 14:21:18','2013-03-21 06:21:18',' ','','','publish','open','open','','122','','','2013-07-17 14:39:17','2013-07-17 06:39:17